        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 16. — Nipponithyris afra Cooper, 1973: A-H, dorsal, lateral and anterior views of complete specimens (MNHN IB-2013-89-91), North-West Madagascar, off Majumga, MIRIKY, stn CP 3252, 850-900 m; I, J, inner views of ventral valve (MNHN IB-2013-92), and tilted (J) to show swollen bases and grooves to accommodate inner socket ridges, SEM, North-West Madagascar, between Majumga and Cap Saint-André, MIRIKY, stn CP 3278, 750-780 m; K, L, inner and oblique views of dorsal valve (MNHN IB-2013-93) to show brachial loop, SEM, Mozambique Channel, Inhambane transect, MAINBAZA, stn CP 3139, 1092-1195 m. Scale bars: A-H, 5 mm; I-L, 2 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4578198/files/figure.png" .

